0.  Have perl5.002 installed.

1.  Read FAQ, SECURITY, README and MODULE_NOTES.

2.  Install all of the modules listed in MODULE_NOTES, making sure
    to understand the notes in MODULE_NOTES and act on them if
    necessary.

3.  Type 'perl Makefile.PL'.

4.  Type 'make'.

5.  Type 'make install'.

6.  Go read misc/HOW_TO_PLAY.

7.  Go read the source code.

8.  Have fun!

9.  When your fun is negatively impacted by errorful features,
    send fsg@coriolan.amicus.com a bug report!
